702316f-a.title: Brooklyn: 4th Avenue - Pacific Street
702316f-a.text:
Fourth Ave., at Pacific Street, showing the erection of the Fourth Ave. Subway, a B.M.T. line. In the center, extending eastward, is the
north side of Pacific Street.
1917.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

702318f-c.title: Brooklyn: 4th Avenue - Pacific Street
702318f-c.text:
1-2
4th Avenue, at the N. W. corner of Pacifio Street, showing the Protestant Episcopal Church of the Redeemer. Also shown is construction work on the Fourth Avenue subway.
1917
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
Another view of the church, years later.
May 11, 1929
P. L. Sperr
